data.description: Lovely two-story Cape Style home on a large private lot on Pleasant Bay.  Situated between the Cape Cod National Golf Course and the Oceanfront Wequassett Resort.  This recently renovated home has three large bedrooms, two full baths and many extras.  Large living room is skylit with cathedral ceiling and French doors that open onto an ample deck.  Eat in kitchen with upgraded appliances, granite countertops and peninsula.  Additional features include a gas fireplace, outdoor shower, and an emergency generator. Laundry in the master bedroom plus additional washer/dryer in basement.  Tankless on-demand water heater.  Generous storage space in easily accessible attic, full basement and extra space in garage.  Septic has been regularly serviced.  This is an ideal year-round home or a vacation get-away.  Sold "AS IS"
